    "longBusinessSummary": "Southern Seed Corporation engages in the research, production, and trading of various crop seeds and agricultural products in Vietnam. It offers various seeds, such as rice, corn, mung bean, flowers, lawn grass, and vegetables. The company provides organic farm produce, including tomato - hot pepper, watermelon, pear shaped melon, cucumber, bitter melon, gourd, pumpkin, loofah, okra, beans, yard long bean, and leaf vegetables. In addition, it offers herbicide MAIZINE and foraxyl fungicide agricultural services, as well as microorganic fertilizers. Further, the company is involved in the import and export, seed testing, and inspection and certification of agricultural seed quality activities. The company was founded in 1976 and is headquartered in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam. Southern Seed Corporation is a subsidiary of Vietnam National Seed Group Joint Stock Company.",
